{"tid":488083,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"也門武裝向阿聯酋核設施發射彈道導彈","createTime":"2017-12-03T11:14:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-03T11:39:41.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"eac12af6651e6e03614831240f4716df20c6490c","tid":488083,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T11:14:38.000Z","msg":"央視新聞客戶端12月3日消息，經也門胡塞武裝向央視記者證實，也門胡塞武裝於當地時間12月3日中午12時15分，向阿聯酋首都阿布扎比的核設施發射了一枚彈道導彈。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5d6d90f3bdd40d6d1fc329da02f23c5b8a0394e","tid":488083,"uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T11:16:35.000Z","msg":"Yemen's Houthi rebels say they have launched a cruise missile towards a nuclear plant in the UAE capital of Abu Dhabi.<br />\n<br />\nAccording to a report in the Saba news agency, the missile hit the Barakah nuclear power station, which is under construction. A website for the Houthi-owned television network al-Masirah also reported the strike.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;The missile force announces the launching of a winged cruise missile ... towards al-Barakah nuclear reactor in Abu Dhabi,&quot; noted a statement on both websites.<br />\n<br />\nNo evidence was provided for the claim and there was no immediate confirmation of the missile launch from the UAE."},{"pid":"8e7dbf99aa747ff0b4a4cfe64cd99158b6bfbaa7","tid":488083,"uid":22199,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T11:17:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"149b536d94a2a7433464d73f2f49136858bbd55f","tid":488083,"uid":53261,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T11:18:39.000Z","msg":"世界大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ed68ba077e7b8dde591882940809499c65a858e","tid":488083,"uid":40470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-03T11:20:01.000Z","msg":"又到連登仔上位做世界霸者既事機<img src=\"/assets/faces/lom